query:
SELECT 
  j.id, 
  j.serviceType, 
  j.status, 
  j.siteAddress, 
  j.customerName,
  j.assignedSupplierId
FROM jobs j
WHERE j.assignedSupplierId = (
  SELECT su.supplierId 
  FROM users u 
  JOIN supplierUsers su ON u.id = su.userId 
  WHERE u.email = '12@supplier.com' 
  LIMIT 1
)
ORDER BY j.id
